article_id:509,category_name:Events,title_name:A Facility Event Revival, A Wish to the Winds, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>The A Wish to the Winds facility event revival, which will feature a new difficulty level, will start <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1561010400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the water element. You&rsquo;ll also be able to build an event-related reward facility for your Halidom!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5ea1de8b57ab1e54cfab3822dddf4426.png"></div><div>An unrelenting gust heralds the unexpected arrival of both hope and catastrophe when the wind siblings Louise and Lowen arrive in the Halidom. With them, however, the ferocious wind dragon Garuda appears&mdash;and she requires a sacrifice! In order to prevent this fate, you must build a Wind Shrine to repel Garuda. Can the Prince and his friends save the wind siblings?</div><div><br></div><div>â– Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1561010400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1561874399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1560924000,update_time1560933408